import React from 'react'
import './App.css'
import Sidebar from './components/Sidebar/Sidebar'
import { BrowserRouter as Router } from 'react-router-dom'
import Expenses from './pages/Expenses/Expenses'

const App = () => {
  return (
    <>
      <Router>
        <Sidebar />
        <Expenses/>
      </Router>
    </>
  )
}

export default App
